genmean: A number of vertical upright objects in a line, or any thing or any action directly or indirectly associated with this.
oldentry: Popular explanation: a line of vertical upright objects.
verblex: 1. To stand in a line with other people who are all waiting for something. English = queue , line up.
nomlex: 1. A line of people who are all waiting for something. English = queue, line.
